    <projectSourceUrl>https://github.com/builtbybel/CleanmgrPlus/</projectSourceUrl>
    <description>Due to a "glitch" in versioning upstream, all packages following version 1.35.1100 will
    not be available as "newest" package in chocolatey. To counter this, a new package "cleanmgr-plus" was created.
    As of now this package is deprecated and cleanmgr-plus is the new package.
</description>
    <summary>Cleanmgr+ is a portable app that builds upon the Microsoft Disk Clean-up Tool (Cleanmgr.exe) by adding additional features and deleting more junk than the Disk Clean-up Tool.</summary>
    <releaseNotes>https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/cleanmgr-plus</releaseNotes>
    <tags>windows cleanup disk-cleanup cleanmgr</tags>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency id="cleanmgr-plus" version="1.37.1170" />
    </dependencies>
  </metadata>
  <files />
</package>
